public abstract class AbstractElementCondition<E>
extends Object
implements org.openqa.selenium.support.ui.ExpectedCondition<E>

Parent class for ExpectedCondition implementations that rely on the presence of a WebElement. If one of the internal checks fails, the failure message is reported in the message property.
